@startuml
[*] --> Off [The system is initially in an off state]
Off --> SetAlarm [User sets an alarm time]
SetAlarm --> AlarmActivated [System activates the alarm when current time matches set alarm time]
AlarmActivated --> TurnOffAlarm [User turns off the activated alarm]
AlarmActivated --> Ringing [System starts ringing the alarm at the set time]
Ringing --> StopRinging [User stops the ringing alarm]
StopRinging --> Off [System returns to an off state for next scheduled alarm]
@enduml
